connect to the machine and open the terminal

sudo su - #for switch to root user

sudo yum install -y #for updating the package

sudo yum insstall httpd #installing apache package

After the installation start the apache service
sudo systemctl start httpd #for starting the service

create a index.html file and put it in /var/www/html
vim /var/www/html/index.html

<html>
<body>
<h1> Hello World </h1>
<body>
</html>

Now save and exit

Then restart the apache service
systemctl restart httpd

Then open the browser and type below URL
http://localhost:8080
